## patchwork layout IV {.smaller}


::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
p_text + {
  p_hist + {
    p_box + p_scatter + plot_layout(ncol = 1) + plot_layout(tag_level = 'new')
  }
} + 
  plot_layout(ncol = 1) +
  plot_annotation(tag_levels = c("1","a"), tag_prefix = "Fig ")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
